Atletico Madrid face Real Madrid in the Champions League quarter-final first leg on Tuesday night . 
  Diego Simeone has turned Atletico around since joining the club in December 2011 . 
  The Argentinian recently extended his contract until 2019 . 
  Atletico won the La Liga title last season and face their rivals in the last eight . 
  Real Madrid beat Atletico 4-0 in last year's Champions League final . 
 